==Tailoring==
Amaranth is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a dyeable {{name|Shirt141|link=Tailoring{{!}}Crop Top Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a pale violet red dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the purple dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*Amaranth is requested by [[Marnie]] in a letter on the 3rd of [[Fall]] for the [[Quests#Cow's Delight|"Cow's Delight" Quest]].  The reward is {{Price|500}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.

